channel.title: Genability Documentation
channel.description: This site contains documentation, how-tos, tutorials, client libraries, and sample code related to Genability's APIs.

item.title: Java Client Library Tutorial Now Available
item.description:
There’s a new tutorial available for our Java library. It goes through the basics of setting up an account and doing a savings analysis in Java. Check it out!

Make sure to download the source code for the tutorial so that you can follow along.

item.title: Welcome to the Genability How-To Page!
item.description:
GET /rest/echo/hello

Welcome to the home page for the Java client library for Genability’s API. We’re just getting started but, in the future, this is where we’ll put everything having to do with our client libraries and APIs, including:

  • Sample code
  • Javadocs / PyDocs / RubyDocs / *Docs
  • Tutorials and How-Tos
  • API specifications

For now, just enjoy the scenery. You can still see our current documentation page here. Links to existing libraries are located here.
